<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Anasayfa</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Sayfa Ortasında Konumlandırma */
        .centered-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 80vh;
            text-align: center;
            background-image: url('https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1673480195911-3075a87738b0?fm=jpg&q=60&w=3000&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8MXx8d2ViJTIwYmFja2dyb3VuZHxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        /* Başlık Tasarımı */
        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: black;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: black;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background-color:white;
        }

        /* Buton Tasarımı */
        .btn-custom {
            font-size: 18px;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background-color:dimgrey;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px;
            width: 250px;
        }

            .btn-custom:hover {
                background-color: black;
            }

        .btn-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

            /* Buton Container Düzeni */
            .btn-container a {
                text-decoration: none;
            }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="centered-container">
        <div>
            <h1>Hoşgeldiniz!</h1>
            <p>Giriş yapmaya hazırsınız. Lütfen aşağıdaki butonlardan birini seçin.</p>
            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Admin")" class="btn-custom">Admin Paneli</a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "User")" class="btn-custom">User Paneli</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
